    "Reviewing your choices on a regular basis ensures you are taking advantage of the continually evolving Cloud. Monitoring ensures you are aware of any deviance from expected performance. Make trade-offs in your architecture to improve performance, such as using compression or caching, or relaxing consistency requirements.",
